*1985年5月6日，麥拓美迪（Metromedia）集團宣布旗下電視台、麥拓美迪製作公司（Metromedia Producers Corp.）售予[[新闻集团_(1979－2013年)|新聞集團]]及[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]<ref name=mm>{{cite news| first =| last =| authorlink =| author =Cole, Robert J | title =Murdoch to buy & TV stations; cost $2 billion| trans_title =| url =http://www.nytimes.com/1985/05/07/business/murdoch-to-buy-tv-stations-cost-2-billion.html?pagewanted=all| format =| newspaper =| location =| publisher =[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]| agency =| id =| page =| date =May 7, 1985| accessdate =| language =| quote =  | archiveurl =| archivedate =}}</ref><ref>[http://www.metromediaradio.net/online-jazz-music-metromedia-radio/wnew-1130-am-legacy-history/ Legacy Metromedia Radio History]. Metromedia Radio. [2016-06-25].</ref>，新聞集團翌日註冊成立'''福斯娛樂集團公司'''（Fox Entertainment Group, Inc.）。
